---
title: Beef Tenderloin with Creamy Pan Sauce plus Roasted Sweet Potato Couscous
description: Let’s hear it for the humble pan sauce! Here, it’s made with fresh garlic, cream cheese, and butter for a drizzly accent to succulent seared pork filet. Everything’s nestled over a hearty bed of toasted pearl couscous, mixed with roasted sweet potato and garnished with scallion. Pork filet may win the prize, but we’re big fans of this best supporting sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/660c5fa89149ba03ec9b063f-0d0534bc.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/664e3b5cb738d70eba6c4b03-en-US.pdf
cuisine: North America
